cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper deals with visual navigation of autonomous vehicles using semantic segmentation of images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics and machine learning, which makes cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely categories as well. The use of semantic segmentation also involves natural language processing, which makes cs.CL (Computation and Language) a possible category. Finally, the paper involves localization, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
